sumolari.utilities
Class ListObject

java.lang.Object
  sumolari.utilities.ListObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
ListObjectArray, ListObjectLinked
public class ListObject
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a List of objects of class Object. This kind of structures can be implemented in different ways, so this class is just a wrapper that can be use regardless which implementation is used internally. This class should not be used to create new objects: it should be used to specify datatypes of parameters and work with Lists of Object in an abstract way.
